---
title: Sloppy Joe Tempeh Sandwich with Roasted Carrot Sticks
description: Tempeh is firm and chewy in texture and is a great meat substitute. We mash and shred ours to create a mouth watering sammie. Be sure to grab some extra napkins!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sloppy-joe-au-tempeh-3de856ca.jpg
